Method Detail

getOntologyForClass

IOntologyHandle getOntologyForClass(java.net.URI classUri)
Given a class URI, this method locates the ontology in which this class is defined.
In case there are multiple such ontologies, than the first one is returned.

Parameters:
classUri - A URI of that class.
Returns:
IOntologyHandler, or null if no appropriate ontology was found for that class.
